desc: Green Planet Supplies is a leading distributor of quality paper and eco-friendly products for the foodservice, janitorial and hospitality industries in the South Florida area.

layout.text: Green Planet Supplies is a leading distributor of quality paper and eco-friendly products for the foodservice, janitorial and hospitality industries. Our products are available to be shipped all over the world which helps us achieve our mission of sustainability and ensures our future generations live on a Green Planet.
